*These insights require cross-tab data and only appear in the Dashboard synthesis:*

- 🔄 AGI per FTE vs. ACV complexity (Delivery Architecture + Revenue Model) — validates whether team productivity matches service depth required
- 🔄 Founder time allocation vs. client concentration (Delivery Architecture + Revenue Model) — reveals whether key account retention depends on founder
