- 🔄 Delivery model complexity vs. margin (Delivery Architecture + Economic Foundation) — shows whether complexity is justified by profitability
- 🔄 Billable ratio vs. payroll efficiency (Delivery Architecture + Economic Foundation) — reveals structural leverage health

